title: Sharpe's Honour [5 of 15]
description:
[b][center][i]Spain 1813[/i][/center]
[/b]

[center]Sharpe is unwittingly caught up in a French plot; he is convicted 
of the murder of a Spanish nobleman and sentenced to death. 
This time he will need more than just his legendary courage to 
survive.  In a desperate attempt to clear his name, Sharpe is f
orced to venture deep into enemy territory to capture La Marquesa, 
a beautiful French spy, who alone can prove his innocence.
Directed by Tom Clegg
Written by Nigel Kneale from the novel by Bernard Cornwell
Starring Sean Bean as Richard Sharpe and Daragh OMalley as Patrick Harper[/center]
